Package: bare
Architecture: amd64
Depends:
Description: Interactive shell in x86_64 Linux assembly
 No libc, no runtime, pure syscalls. Single static binary.
 8 microsecond startup. Features include dynamic prompt with
 git integration, tab completion with LS_COLORS, syntax
 highlighting, job control, aliases, bookmarks, themes,
 plugin system, and more.
